General.Name: Hwaseung R&A Co. Ltd.
General.Description: Hwaseung R&A Co., Ltd. primarily produces and sells automobile parts worldwide. The company offers weather strip products, including front and rear glass molding products, hood weather strips, sun roof weather strips, glass run products, fixed weather strips, door opening weather strips, door seal and door drip weather strips, trunk lids, and inner and outer door belts. It also provides air conditioning, power steering return, fuel, radiator, brake vacuum, heater, fuel filler, power steering pressure, hydraulic brake, and intercooler hoses. Hwaseung R&A Co., Ltd. is based in Yangsan, South Korea.
